Installs and configures UAMS Client

##### <a name="-uamsclient--uams_local_pkg_path"></a>`uams_local_pkg_path`

Data type: `String[1]`

Path to temporary UAMS directory

Default value: `$uamsclient::params::uams_local_pkg_path`

##### <a name="-uamsclient--install_pkg_url"></a>`install_pkg_url`

Data type: `String[1]`

URL to UAMS Client installer

Default value: `$uamsclient::params::install_pkg_url`

##### <a name="-uamsclient--dev_container_test"></a>`dev_container_test`

Data type: `Boolean`

Indicates if it is a container installation

Default value: `$uamsclient::params::dev_container_test`

##### <a name="-uamsclient--uamsclient_work_dir"></a>`uamsclient_work_dir`

Data type: `String[1]`

Path to UAMS Client workdir

Default value: `$uamsclient::params::uamsclient_work_dir`

##### <a name="-uamsclient--uamsclient_ctl"></a>`uamsclient_ctl`

Data type: `String[1]`

Path to uamsclient-ctl binary

Default value: `$uamsclient::params::uamsclient_ctl`

##### <a name="-uamsclient--uams_access_token"></a>`uams_access_token`

Data type: `String[1]`

UAMS Client access token

Default value: `undef`

##### <a name="-uamsclient--swo_url"></a>`swo_url`

Data type: `String[1]`

SWO URL to the desired endpoint

Default value: `undef`

##### <a name="-uamsclient--uams_metadata"></a>`uams_metadata`

Data type: `Optional[String[1]]`

UAMS Client installation metadata

Default value: `undef`

##### <a name="-uamsclient--uams_override_hostname"></a>`uams_override_hostname`

Data type: `Optional[String[1]]`

Optional variable to set a custom Agent name. By default, Agent name is set to the hostname.

Default value: `undef`

##### <a name="-uamsclient--uams_managed_locally"></a>`uams_managed_locally`

Data type: `Optional[Boolean]`

Optional variable is used to set Agent as managed locally by configuration file.

Default value: `undef`

##### <a name="-uamsclient--local_config_template_parameters"></a>`local_config_template_parameters`

Data type: `Optional[Hash]`

Optional variable to set a hash with variables used to fill local config template file.

Default value: `{ }`
